task.summary: Hooked duel controller up to main
Event handling is now done locally
Event loop added to duel controller
Buttons now change appearance when you hover over them
duel controller now takes two opponents as input
Added in player and enemy images
Added adjustable height ratios for shadows on the duelling sprites
Added another dictionary to control shadow behaviour
Shadows are now manipulated by their width/height ratios
Playing with the ratios to make the shadows look good
Added update function to progress bar
Progress bars now update and can be filled with an assigned value
Fixed duplicate parts on the spritesheet
Created label class and defined a global font
font is loaded on game initialising
Calculates max xp for that level correctly now
Added a button cooldown to stop callback being run multiple times
Made a crude attacking system for now
